def read_data(file):
  xc = pd.read_json(get_file(file), orient='records')
  return xc

def cleanup(data):
  data = data[['pilot', 'pointStart', 'stats', 'takeoff', 'glider']]
  return data

def extract_dict(data, column):
  data_extracted = data[column].apply(pd.Series)
  return data_extracted

def clean_pilot(data):
  data = data[['id', 'username', 'countryIso', 'isMale']]
  data = data.rename(columns={'id':'idPilot', 'countryIso':'fromCountry'})
  return data

def clean_takeoff(data):
  data = data[['name', 'countryIso']]
  data = data.rename(columns={'name':'takeoffName', 'countryIso':'takeoffCountry'})
  return data

def clean_glider(data):
  data = data[['name', 'nameProducer', 'subclass']]
  data = data.rename(columns={'name':'gliderName', 'nameProducer':'gliderProducer', 'subclass':'gliderClass'})
  return data

def clean_pointStart(data):
  data = data.rename(columns={'time':'takeoffTime'})
  return data

def clean_stats(data):
  data = data.rename(columns={'duration':'flightDuration'})
  return data

def combine_frames(data1, data2, original_column):
  final_data = pd.concat([data1, data2], axis=1).drop(original_column, axis=1)
  return final_data

def delete_NO_glider(data):
  data = data[data.gliderProducer.map(len) > 1]
  return data

def order_descending(data, series):
  data = data.sort_values(series, ascending=False)
  return data

def give_month(takeoff):
  s = takeoff[5:7]
  month_to_name = {'01': 4, '02':5, '03': 6, '04':7, 
                   '05':8, '06':9, '07':10, '08':11, '09':12,
                   '10':1, '11':2, '12':3}
  return month_to_name[s]
  
months = ['October', 'November', 'December', 'January', 'February', 'March', 'April', 'May', 'June', 'July', 'August',
          'September']

def get_month_index(month):
  return month-1

def get_country_index(country):
  return country_idx[country]

def clean_time(time):
  time = time[2:4] + ":" + time[5:7] + ":" + time[8:10]
  return time

def date_datetime(column):
  column = pd.to_datetime(column)       #.dt.time
  return column

def find_mistake_time(time):
  if time[6] == "-":
    return False
  else:
    return True

def define_time_categories(time):
  if time[0] != '0' and time[3] in ['0', '1', '2']:
    t = int(time[0:2]) + 0.5
  elif time[0] == '0' and time[3] in ['0', '1', '2']:
    t = int(time[1]) + 0.5
  elif time[0] == '0' and time[3] in ['3', '4', '5']:
    t = int(time[1]) + 0.9
  elif time[0] != '0' and time[3] in ['3', '4', '5']:
    t = int(time[0:2]) + 0.9
  return t

time_categories = ['0:30', '1:00', '1:30', '2:00', '2:30', '3:00', '3:30', '4:00', '4:30', '5:00', '5:30', '6:00', 
                   '6:30', '7:00', '7:30', '8:00', '8:30', '9:00', '9:30', '10:00', '10:30', '11:00']

def make_delta_time(time):
  h, m, s = time.split(':')
  return datetime.timedelta(hours=int(h), minutes=int(m), seconds=int(s))

def round_to_minutes(time):
  return time.round(freq='5min')

def return_to_time(number):
  number = pd.TimedeltaIndex(number, unit='m')
  return number

def myplot(graph, graph_title):
  graph = graph[graph.index < pd.Timedelta(seconds=4*3600)]
  ax = graph.plot(figsize=(25,15), title=graph_title, color=['#ffc785', '#df7599', '#7189bf']) 
  # vals = ax.get_yticks()
  # ax.set_yticklabels(['{}%'.format(x) for x in vals])

def myplot_xc(graph, graph_title):
  graph = graph[graph.index < pd.Timedelta(seconds=7*3600)]
  ax = graph.plot(figsize=(25,15), title=graph_title, color=['#ffc785', '#df7599', '#7189bf']) 
  # vals = ax.get_yticks()
  # ax.set_yticklabels(['{:.2f}%'.format(x) for x in vals])

def get_percents(amount):
  amount_perc = amount / sum(amount)*100
  return amount_perc

def get_progressive_perc(data):
  pilots_sum = data.pilots_sum.sum()
  prog_sum = data.pilots_sum.sum()
  prog_perc_zero = (pilots_sum / pilots_sum) * 100
  prog_perc_list = [prog_perc_zero]
  prog_sum_list = [pilots_sum]
  for i in range(1, len(data.pilots_sum)):
    prog_sum = (prog_sum - data.pilots_sum[i-1])
    prog_perc = round((prog_sum / pilots_sum * 100), 1)
    prog_perc_list.append(prog_perc)
    prog_sum_list.append(prog_sum)
  data['ProgressivePerc'] = prog_perc_list
  data['ProgressiveSum'] = prog_sum_list
  return data

def is_home_flight(data):
  data['homeFlight'] = True
  for i in range(data.shape[0]):
    if data.takeoffCountry.iloc[i] != data.fromCountry.iloc[i]:
      data.homeFlight.iloc[i] = False
  return data

for year in xc_years:
  year.flightDuration = year.flightDuration.map(clean_time)
  year.flightDuration = year.flightDuration.map(make_delta_time)
  year['TimeCategory'] = year.flightDuration.map(round_to_minutes)
  year["takeoffMonth"] = year.takeoffTime.map(give_month)
  year = is_home_flight(year)
  year = year[year.TimeCategory > datetime.timedelta(minutes=0)]

  year_desc = order_descending(year, 'flightDuration')
  pilots = year_desc.drop_duplicates(subset=['idPilot'])
  unique_pilots_years.append(pilots)
  pilots_count = pilots.shape[0]
  unique_pilots_years_count.append(pilots_count)

  home_flights = year[year.homeFlight == True]
  home_flights_count = year[year.homeFlight == True].shape[0]
  home_flights_years.append(home_flights)

# How many people fly particular brand of glider

glider_brands_years = []
for year in unique_pilots_years:
  cleared_gliders = delete_NO_glider(year)
  glider_brand = cleared_gliders.groupby('gliderProducer').gliderProducer.count()
  glider_brands_years.append(glider_brand)

graph = pd.concat({'2018': glider_brands_years[0], '2019': glider_brands_years[1], '2020': glider_brands_years[2]}, axis=1).sort_values('2019', ascending=False)
graph = graph[:20]
ax = graph.plot.bar(title="The brands of gliders pilots fly", color=['#ffc785', '#df7599', '#7189bf'], figsize=(15,15))
